    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/eb0626278b3f2f5f4a4202fb3f06e4ad.webp?t=1762714346\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/e12a47971b98f3cd095992e55eff186c.avif?t=1762714346\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>♥ 地狱般的爱情故事♥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✟我可爱的魅魔✟ - 这是一部以基督教地狱为背景的视觉宗教讽刺小说，是一款休闲三消游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>♥ 为你的罪下地狱 ♥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 并认识✟你可爱的魅魔✟！她真的需要你的帮助！ 地狱深陷没落，所有控制系统都被摧毁，魔族早已无法应对新来罪人的灵魂折磨。 只有你能帮助魅魔完成购买凡人灵魂的月度计划！ 你的任务非常简单——说服一个年轻的虔诚修女将她不朽的灵魂卖给魔鬼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/cf6b3eb29f4702aa3a5ea493e2d1e87b.poster.avif?t=1762714346\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/cf6b3eb29f4702aa3a5ea493e2d1e87b.webm?t=1762714346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/cf6b3eb29f4702aa3a5ea493e2d1e87b.mp4?t=1762714346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>♥ 你的灵魂将永远在地狱燃烧 ♥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >, 您将能够遇到地狱中最可爱、最危险的居民：篡位者、独裁者，甚至是苏共中央主席。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希特勒和斯大林在地狱的第 8 圈感到无聊，期待着最后的审判。 更好地了解他们并找出他们在死亡期间的行为动机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/d21d27cabf9eadedda061308e2ac307f.poster.avif?t=1762714346\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/d21d27cabf9eadedda061308e2ac307f.webm?t=1762714346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/d21d27cabf9eadedda061308e2ac307f.mp4?t=1762714346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>⛧魅魔⛧ - 她是一个可爱的地狱少女，渴望最终冲破地狱第八圈，转往更有前途的部门工作。 为了事业的发展，她愿意做任何事情，即使是作为 恶魔 的兼职工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✟德蕾莎修女✟ - 她是洛雷托爱尔兰修女会的一位年轻无辜的修女。 她全心相信上帝，并准备将自己的全部奉献给修道院工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>♥ 特征 ♥:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 基督教环境中的地狱爱情故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 三消游戏的经典视觉小说</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 11 个充满活力的 Live2d 动画</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 动画 3D 背景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 多重结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 伟大的 Lofi 嘻哈由 G374 和 smth.nothing ♥</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719660/extras/87fcff5d73bad7068219e9c44fad15d0.webp?t=1762714346\" width=616 height=10 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game does not contain non-tolerance, any religious of any political organizations and anything like that. Only love and mutual understanding. <strong>Make Match3, not war ♥</strong></p>",
